{"tid":1867802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫護暫停罷工啦！香港人你哋點對得住醫護手足","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:54.000Z","uid":180808,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dba2c03367487fdf2334fe5258ea6274e5c21e95","tid":1867802,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"醫管局企硬唔讓步<br />\n又冇其他工會響應一齊罷工<br />\n搞到醫護兩面不是人<br />\n被逼復工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足肯定俾醫管局秋後算帳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由8月開始講大三罷<br />\n點解依家醫護手足肯帶頭罷足成個星期<br />\n都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係啦香港人<br />\n繼續2盒thx啦<br />\n繼續同阿婆一齊搶米搶廁紙啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港好快</span></strong>   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decab5ebbf27a8b316f76b6bd1529cbe9f3dd112","tid":1867802,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dba2c03367487fdf2334fe5258ea6274e5c21e95","tid":1867802,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"醫管局企硬唔讓步<br />\n又冇其他工會響應一齊罷工<br />\n搞到醫護兩面不是人<br />\n被逼復工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足肯定俾醫管局秋後算帳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由8月開始講大三罷<br />\n點解依家醫護手足肯帶頭罷足成個星期<br />\n都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係啦香港人<br />\n繼續2盒thx啦<br />\n繼續同阿婆一齊搶米搶廁紙啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港好快</span></strong>   <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"【醫護罷工第5日】工會表決擱置罷工 逾6,000人投票過半支持復工<br />\n<br />\n//新一輪投票要超過6,000名會員支持，才會